{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "36e0bfdf-9241-46a8-95b4-d224b1501bae",
    "name": "Bata Analytics Dashboard APIs",
    "description": "All 27 dashboard analytics endpoints under /api/v1/analytics/, plus the generic /api/v1/chat-with-data/query agent endpoint. Join across bata_master_trigger + bata_insights_v2 via bata_master_trigger.callUuid = bata_insights_v2.call_uuid.\n\n**Common filter params (all optional):**\n- `start_date` / `end_date` — YYYY-MM-DD (default: last 90 days)\n- `gmbStoreCode` — e.g. 3625\n- `state` — e.g. Delhi\n- `city` — e.g. Chennai\n- `area` — area name\n- `store` — businessName e.g. \"Bata Shoe Store\"\n- `businessId` — numeric businessId\n- `intent` — e.g. Complaint, Stock Availability\n- `sentiment` — Positive | Neutral | Negative\n\n**Chat With Data (NL → report):**\nThe `/api/v1/chat-with-data/query` endpoint takes a natural-language question and returns a markdown report backed by the caller's `{client}_insights_v2` table. The active client is resolved from the API key, so the same endpoint serves bata, dhl, and any future client without code changes.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "35399501"
  },
